title: Lynyrd Skynyrd LIVE - Louisville,KY. (2007)
description:
Re-Upped from an earlier mishap.....

Lynyrd Skynyrd LIVE at the Freedom Hall in Louisville, Kentucky on June 15th, 2007. This is a re-broadcast of a live concert of the band during their 2007 concert tour. This show was originally broadcast in HD and has been re-encoded for your viewing pleasure! 

Including members from the original band that survived the plane crash, Lynyrd Skynyrd brings their Southern Rock-n-Roll style to the stage. Songs include "Simple Man", "Free Bird", "Sweet Home Alabama", and more.

This concert is unique in part due to the incorporation of concert footage from the original band back in the &#039;70&#039;s and played on the big screen behind the current bandmates and in sync with the current song list!


Format: xvid, mp3
Resolution: 624x352 HD WS
Run Time: 1:27:28
Frame Rate: 29fps
